<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; color:#000000; bEditID:r3st1; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; text-align: right;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; "><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000066" size="6">{!Contact.SchoolText__c}</font></span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; text-align: right;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="'Times New Roman', Times, serif" color="#ff6600" size="4"><i>Chartered By The British Schools Foundation</i></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; text-align: right;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif" color="#c0c0c0" size="6"><b><i><br></i></b></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; text-align: right;"><font style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="border-spacing: 5px;">Dear&nbsp;{!Contact.Salutation} {!Contact.LastName},</span></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="border-spacing: 5px;"><br></span></font></div><div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font>The health and safety of your children is our top priority. In addition to taking all necessary&nbsp;</font>precautions, we aim to always keep our parents well informed of anything which comes to our&nbsp;attention which may affect your children.</font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font>I am writing to inform you that there has been a confirmed case of hand, foot and mouth disease in a&nbsp;</font>pupil in one of our Year 3 classes. Hand, foot and mouth disease is a contagious, viral infection which&nbsp;spreads if contaminated droplets or bodily fluids are transferred from an infected person. Symptoms&nbsp;include cold-like symptoms such as: loss of appetite, headache, fatigue, irritability, cough, a&nbsp;moderately high temperature, a non-itchy red rash and painful mouth ulcers. Hand-foot- and mouth&nbsp;disease may cause all of the above signs and symptoms or just a few of them. Please seek immediate&nbsp;medical advice and advis</font><span style="font-size: large; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">e </span><font face="Arial, sans-serif">the school promptly if your child is unwell with any of the above symptoms.</font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif">At school, we are taking all precautions necessary including:</font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div><ul><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Ensuring all classrooms are disinfected with both ultra-violet light and a disinfectant</font></li></ul></div><div><ul><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Good ventilation of classrooms and other rooms</font></li></ul></div><div><ul><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Daily cleaning and disinfection of the door handles, stair railings, toys, bathroom accessories&nbsp;and food utensils</font></li></ul></div><div><ul><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Early Yearsâ€™ toys thoroughly disinfected every Friday</font></li></ul></div><div><ul><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Unwell children will see nurse and if necessary parents will be contacted</font></li></ul></div><div><ul><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">The children have been taught how to wash their hands by teachers</font></li></ul></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif">If you believe your child has hand, foot and mouth disease, please seek medical treatment, follow&nbsp;safety procedures at home and keep them away from school until they have recovered from the&nbsp;illness.</font></div></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif">For further information about hand, foot and mouth disease, please see the link below:</font></div></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial;"><a href="http://www.nhs.uk/Conditions/Hand-foot-and-mouth-disease/Pages/Introduction.aspx">http://www.nhs.uk/Conditions/Hand-foot-and-mouth-disease/Pages/Introduction.aspx</a><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial;"><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4">Kind Regards</font></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4"><br></font></div><div><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4">Alison Mackey</font></span></div><div><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4">Deputy Head of Primary</font></span></div></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial;"><p dir="ltr" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><br></p><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">{!Contact.SchoolText__c}</span></div></div></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><i><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#ff6600"><b>World Class Education</b></font></i></span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; text-align: center;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="1">{!User.School_List_Email_Footer__c}</font><font class="Apple-style-span" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="1">&nbsp;</font></div>]]></td>
